data.description: Welcome to 460 Starr Lane, Deeth, Nevada, 89823 " a charming home. Step inside to discover the warmth of wood-adorned walls that create a cozy and inviting atmosphere throughout the house. The residence has four bedrooms, providing ample space for family and guests, with two full bathrooms. Pellet Stove insert in the living room. The property is not only about the interior; it's also designed for outdoor living. Two storage sheds and a pump house, complete with a new filter case installed in the summer of 2023. For those with recreational vehicles, this property is equipped with 50-amp RV hook-ups, providing a convenient and accessible way to enjoy the open road. Whether you're enjoying the cool shade of the wood-lined interiors or basking in the warmth of the summer sun, 460 Starr Lane offers a comfortable living environment for every season.
